Wilderness Scout
The Wilderness Scout is a master of survival beyond the city walls: tracker,
hunter, and guide through the untamed wilderness of Rifts Earth. Where soldiers
march in formation, the Scout moves alone and unseen.

Scouts receive a large package of survival and tracking skills from the start,
leaving fewer picks for supplemental training. They are the best navigators and
animal trackers in the game.

Attribute requirements: None. Any OCC-eligible race may choose Wilderness Scout.
Starting equipment: Hunting rifle or shotgun, hunting knife, survival backpack,
camouflage clothing, compass, fire-starting kit, and one week of rations.
